name: DishTracker
0:
”Alexa, tell Dish Tracker that the dishes are dirty.”
”Alexa, ask Dish Tracker for the status of my dishes.”
”Alexa, tell Dish Tracker that I washed the dishes.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dish tracker
des:
"Dish Tracker" can help you remember if the dishes in your dishwasher are clean or dirty.

When you put dirty dishes into the dishwasher, just say, "Alexa, tell Dish Tracker that the dishes are dirty."

Later, when you forgot if those dishes are clean or dirty, just ask, "Alexa, ask Dish Tracker for the status of my dishes." I'll reply with the clean/dirty status and time you last updated that status.

Unfortunately, I can't talk directly to your dishwasher, so you'll have to keep me updated every time you load and unload.

Visit www.jeffdelaney.com/contact/ with suggestions or errors
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
